g.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcharanzova%2Fstatus%2F1389628144987029506&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=53436567\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcharanzova%2Fstatus%2F1389628144987029506&h=61f3eaa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/charanzova/status/1389628144987029506</a><br />\n<br />\n🔹Sandro Gozi<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sandrogozi/status/1389644895086948357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsandrogozi%2Fstatus%2F1389644895086948357&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=439d9954\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsandrogozi%2Fstatus%2F1389644895086948357&h=729c4125\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/sandrogozi/status/1389644895086948357</a><br />\n<br />\n🔹Reinhard B&uuml;tikofer<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/bueti/status/1389622243987181572\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbueti%2Fstatus%2F1389622243987181572&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=53f1972a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbueti%2Fstatus%2F1389622243987181572&h=8ea7bc7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/bueti/status/1389622243987181572</a><br />\n<br />\n🔹Guy Verhofstadt<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/guyverhofstadt/status/1389636323645005824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fguyverhofstadt%2Fstatus%2F1389636323645005824&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=5d0275d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fguyverhofstadt%2Fstatus%2F1389636323645005824&h=89a57384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/guyverhofstadt/status/1389636323645005824</a><br />\n<br />\n其他議員<br />\n🔸Tom Tugendhat<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TomTugendhat/status/138962151766794240