moji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:38:57.000Z","msg":"咪就係, 鄭月娥教曉我們的事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:48:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7376d37eb0944c54a69c0ba1e6a229812b461e5","tid":2516842,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12cc92a2f0627afdf905d5eeff12b184d149a93c","tid":2516842,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:47:44.000Z","msg":"撤回先講，同當年暫緩送中條例一樣<br />\n過左再搞又點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187be01a36f3c472e37678e1a44e64ecfa04b6b3","tid":2516842,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12cc92a2f0627afdf905d5eeff12b184d149a93c","tid":2516842,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:47:44.000Z","msg":"撤回先講，同當年暫緩送中條例一樣<br />\n過左再搞又點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:49:29.000Z","msg":"TG見到, 呢個好笑<br />\n撤回? 似曾相識？<br />\n<br />\n港府擬要求續約或新到港外傭強制接種疫苗，勞福局局長羅致光更豪言：「佢（外傭）可以選擇唔喺香港做嘢」，惹來菲律賓和印尼領事不滿，觸發外交風波。作風強硬的特首林鄭月娥昨突然褪軚，稱聽到社會意見，強調措施未有定案，已要求勞福局重新檢視。<br />\n<br />\n移工團體質疑林鄭出口術暫緩打針，要求白紙黑字承諾撤回。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3egd1Tx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3egd1Tx&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=1b13ec85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3egd1Tx</a>"},{"pid":"f633a7edb5a85b1a69d3d95c0125724bbf84d619","tid":2516842,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"187be01a36f3c472e37678e1a44e64ecfa04b6b3","tid":2516842,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12cc92a2f0627afdf905d5eeff12b184d149a93c","tid":2516842,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:47:44.000Z","msg":"撤回先講，同當年暫緩送中條例一樣<br />\n過左再搞又點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:49:29.000Z","msg":"TG見到, 呢個好笑<br />\n撤回? 似曾相識？<br />\n<br />\n港府擬要求續約或新到港外傭強制接種疫苗，勞福局局長羅致光更豪言：「佢（外傭）可以選擇唔喺香港做嘢」，惹來菲律賓和印尼領事不滿，觸發外交風波。作風強硬的特首林鄭月娥昨突然褪軚，稱聽到社會意見，強調措施未有定案，已要求勞福局重新檢視。<br />\n<br />\n移工團體質疑林鄭出口術暫緩打針，要求白紙黑字承諾撤回。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3egd1Tx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3egd1Tx&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=1b13ec85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3egd1Tx</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:00:04.000Z","msg":"語言偽術，總之見到暫停暫緩<br />\n唔可以叫成功，係要佢完全收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"6507931e43f06d5035af27f54af3235ced7da1b2","tid":2516842,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:36:10.000Z","msg":"歐洲藥管局正加速審視科興數據<br />\n導致22名香港接種者死亡但仍堅稱自己沒有不良反應的科興現時仍然未獲歐盟批准，但歐洲藥品管理局剛剛表示，已開始針對科興疫苗進行「滾動式審核」（rolling review），以歐盟標準檢視科興疫苗的有效性、安全性、品質，成為歐盟首隻審核的強國疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n聲明雖然沒有提到預計審核時間，但表示所需時間較正常快，並稱根據實驗室數據及臨床研究的初步數據，科興能產生一定抗體，歐盟藥品管理局則會評估是否利多於弊，再考慮是否向科興批出上市許可（marketing authorisation application，MAA）。<br />\n<br />\n科興疫苗自推出以來，一直在全球各地爭議不斷，不但多次延遲公開臨床數據，而且對於武肺的保護效力只有50.4%，遠低於其他國家研發的疫曲。土耳其、巴西、智利大力推廣接種科興疫苗，但武漢肺炎確診數字不減反增，令人質疑接種科興是否真係「利多於弊」。<br />\n<br />\n更恐怖的是，即使接種了科興，亦不代表接種者代代平常，過去兩名智利主教即使接種兩劑科興疫苗後，仍然確診武漢肺炎，甚至連中國疾控中心主任高福上月初亦表示，「中國疫苗的保護力不高」，當局須採取混針的方式，去提升效力。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，即使已有27名香港人在接種科興疫苗後不治，大陸衛健委上月底竟然仍然可以公然表示「官方至今未有通報種後死亡報告」，令人質疑科興疫苗向歐盟提交的資料是否完整。<br />\n<br />\n為了防止科興透過「造假數」形式，欺騙當局打入歐盟，大家可積極分享香港人接觸科興後不幸逝世的新聞 ，以防強國疫苗蒙混過關。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://twitter.com/EMA_News/status/1389513666672869376\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEMA_News%2Fstatus%2F1389513666672869376&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=f70ff0a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEMA_News%2Fstatus%2F1389513666672869376&h=2807180d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/EMA_News/status/1389513666672869376</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/AFP/status/1389540951194996740\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAFP%2Fstatus%2F1389540951194996740&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=ddf9d04c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAFP%2Fstatus%2F1389540951194996740&h=c2fe83b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/AFP/status/1389540951194996740</a></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://t.me/HKinternational\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKinternational&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=f00869ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKinternational</a>"}}